  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Surface_conditions_mim  Entity: visual_appearance_representation  Where: WR11 
   <express_ref linkend="surface_conditions:mim:Surface_conditions_mim.visual_appearance_representation.wr:WR11"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.visual_appearance_representation.wr:WR11">
Each instance of <b>visual_appearance_representation</b> shall be referenced by exactly one <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.property_definition_representation"/>. 
This <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.property_definition_representation"/> shall relate the representation with a <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.property_definition"/> that is the <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.general_property_association.derived_definition"/> of a <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.general_property_association"/> that refers as <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.general_property_association.base_definition"/> to a <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.general_property"/>, which is a surface condition. 
</ext_description>

	
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Surface_conditions_mim  Rule: restrict_representation_for_surface_condition 
   <express_ref linkend="surface_conditions:mim:Surface_conditions_mim.restrict_representation_for_surface_condition"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.restrict_representation_for_surface_condition">
The <b>restrict_representation_for_surface_condition</b> rule enforces that the instance of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> that provides the values of a particular kind of surface condition be associated with the appropriate instance of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.property_definition"/>.
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.restrict_representation_for_surface_condition.wr:WR1">
there shall not be any instance of <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.property_definition_representation"/> such that the represented property identifies a particular kind of surface condition and such the <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.property_definition_representation.used_representation"/> is not the representation appropriate for this kind of surface condition.
</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Surface_conditions_mim  Rule: restrict_treatment_result 
   <express_ref linkend="surface_conditions:mim:Surface_conditions_mim.restrict_treatment_result"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.restrict_treatment_result">
The <b>restrict_treatment_result</b> rule constrains the content of a <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> that fulfills the requirement of a <express_ref linkend="Surface_conditions:arm:Surface_conditions_arm.Treatment_result"/>. 
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.restrict_treatment_result.wr:WR1">
Each instance of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> that has a name of 'treatment result' shall contain at most 2 <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item"/> instances in its set of items. 
These <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item"/> instances shall be of type <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/>. 
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.restrict_treatment_result.wr:WR2">
Exactly one <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item"/> shall have a name of 'result'.
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.restrict_treatment_result.wr:WR3">
At most one <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item"/> shall have a name of 'purpose'. 
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.material_for_coating_layer">
The <b>material_for_coating_layer</b> rule constrains instances of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> with name 'coating layer', 
to  be referred to by exactly one <express_ref linkend="material_property_definition_schema:ir_express:material_property_definition_schema.material_designation"/> that specifies the material they are made of.
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.material_for_coating_layer.wr:WR1">
There shall not be any instance of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> with name 'coating layer' that is not referred to by exactly one <express_ref linkend="material_property_definition_schema:ir_express:material_property_definition_schema.material_designation"/>.
</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Surface_conditions_mim  Function: surface_condition_correlation 
   <express_ref linkend="surface_conditions:mim:Surface_conditions_mim.surface_condition_correlation"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.surface_condition_correlation">
The <b>surface_condition_correlation</b> function returns FALSE if, in the case where the name attribute of an instance of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.property_definition"/> is one of the names associated with the representation of surface conditions, the instance of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> has a different name. 
<p>If the names are the same, the function returns TRUE. 
If the name of the <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.property_definition"/> is not in the list of names of surface conditions, the function returns UNKNOWN. 
</p>
	</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.surface_condition_correlation.pd">
the <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.property_definition"/> that is considered.
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Surface_conditions_mim.surface_condition_correlation.rep">
the <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> that is considered.
</ext_description>
</ext_descriptions>
